data.name: UnoControlRoadmapModel
desc: specifies the standard model of a UnoControlContainer.
**since**
OOo 2.1

properties.name: BackgroundColor
desc: specifies the background color (RGB) of the control.
The Default value is white

properties.name: Border
desc: specifies the border style of the control.

properties.name: Complete
desc: determines whether the control container is complete or not.
If it is false than a non - interactive RoadmapItem is appended

properties.name: CurrentItemID
desc: refers to the ID of the currently selected item.
Initially this property is set to \"-1\" which is equal to \"undefined\" If the Roadmap Item that the CurrentItemID refers to is removed the property \"CurrentItemID\" is set to -1

properties.name: Graphic
desc: specifies a graphic to be displayed on the control
If this property is present, it interacts with the ImageURL in the following way:
**since**
OOo 2.1

properties.name: HelpText
desc: specifies the help text of the control.

properties.name: HelpURL
desc: specifies the help URL of the control.

properties.name: ImageURL
desc: specifies a URL to an image to use for the control.
The image is placed in the lower right corner of the control

properties.name: Interactive
desc: determines whether the control is interactive or not.
A roadmap control which is interactive allows selecting its items out-of-order, by simply clicking them.

properties.name: Printable
desc: specifies whether the control will be printed with the document.

properties.name: Text
desc: specifies the text displayed in the control.
